# Session workflow — Check Your Backup (desktop app)

Extends `hola-adios-global.mdc`. This file is **only for the Python desktop app repo**,
not for the marketing website.

> **Install:** copy this file to the desktop app repo as `.cursor/rules/hola-adios-project.mdc`
> together with `hola-adios-global.mdc` (from checkyourbackup-website).

Read `AGENTS.md` or `README.md` in the desktop repo for exact commands.

