## Project profile

- **Type:** Python desktop application (Windows + macOS)
- **Version source:** `pyproject.toml`, `version.py`, or `__init__.py` — adjust path below
- **Build output:** `.exe` / `.app` / portable zips (paths vary — fill in after audit)
- **Distribution:** GitHub Releases via `CheckYourBackup/downloads` repo
- **Website sync:** update `downloads/releases.js` in **checkyourbackup-website** when publishing

